profile_positions.description:
• Managing full recruitment process from identifying, sourcing and attracting top candidates all the way to interviewing and hiring for mainly our Hotels department in the Benelux, the Nordics and Germany (Entry level through senior management positions);
• Sourcing candidates through job boards, social media, networking events and career fairs;
• Pre-screen potential candidates;
• Conduct interviews and set up interviews with Hiring Manager;
• Organize and conduct assessments;
• Build up and maintain good relationship with Hiring Managers;
• Identifying the need for changes in recruitment process and make suggestions for improvement
• Consult with the hiring managers to understand specific needs for each role;
• Close collaboration with Hiring Managers, HR Advisory and sourcing partners;
• Handle the negotiation process.
